---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
---

<Base title="企業理念・行動指針 – SIA Digital Technology">
  <PageHero title="企業理念・行動指針" />
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-14">
    <div class="prose-body">
      <blockquote><p>企業理念</p></blockquote>
      <p><strong>S– To serve the public&nbsp;</strong><em>社会への貢献</em></p>
      <p><strong>I- Independent research and development&nbsp;</strong><em>独立した思考、独立した研究開発を意味します</em></p>
      <p><strong>A- A grade product&nbsp;</strong><em>商品が最高レベルであることを意味します</em></p>
      <p><strong>D- Data&nbsp;</strong><em>未来の世界は、無数のデータによって構築されるだろう</em></p>
      <p><strong>T- Technology&nbsp;</strong><em>日本の伝統を守り、未来を創造するためにテクノロジーを活用します</em></p>

      <div class="h-16" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <blockquote><p>行動指針</p></blockquote>
      <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-[26%_auto] md:items-start">
        <figure class="!my-0"><img src="/images/desk.webp" alt="" width="350" height="233" loading="lazy" /></figure>
        <div>
          <p><strong>ＳＩＡデジタルテクノロジー株式会社</strong> 2022年7月設立。AIとIoTデジタル技術で、日本の伝統を守りながら未来を創ります。</p>
          <p>Microsoft、Alibaba、Tencentなどで20年以上のAI・クラウド経験を持つチームです。 日本の伝統を尊重し、中小企業の現実的な課題に寄り添いながら、AI活用を無理なく進めます。</p>
          <p>社員IDは1000番からスタート AIの時代に「巨人の肩」に立つために。 私たちはAIをパートナーとし、使いこなすことで一人ひとりが「1000倍」の価値を生み出します。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p>Our company was established in July 2022 with a vision to transform the world through AI and digital technology, making life better for all Japanese people.</p>
      <p>Our team comprises experts with nearly 20 years of professional experience, hailing from leading global AI and cloud computing companies such as Microsoft, Alibaba, and Tencent.</p>
      <p>We deeply value the importance of preserving Japanese traditions while understanding the critical challenges faced by small and medium-sized businesses today. We look forward to collaborating with our clients to leverage AI technology and create a better future together.</p>
      <p>At our company, employee ID numbers begin at 1000.This reflects our belief that we stand on the shoulders of the giant known as the age of Artificial Intelligence.We recognize that AI will fundamentally transform the future workplace, and that without the power of AI, the value of human work would shrink to single digits. Therefore, every member of SIA Digital Technology is seen as a partner in building the future together with AI—someone who creates the value of “1000” by fully harnessing the capabilities of artificial intelligence.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Base>
